        "email": "paf@cray.com",
        "username": "paf",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-01-28 21:22:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nWith this patch in, running mmstress (which does a lot of page faulting), I see threads stuck waiting on the page bit:\n\nsleep_on_page+0xe/0x20; wait_on_page_bit+0x74/0x80; vvp_io_fault_start+0x855/0xc20 [lustre]; cl_io_start+0x72/0x140 [obdclass]; cl_io_loop+0xac/0x1a0 [obdclass]; ll_page_mkwrite+0x280/0x6c0 [lustre]; __do_fault+0xe7/0x570; handle_pte_fault+0xa4/0xcc0; handle_mm_fault+0x1ae/0x240; do_page_fault+0x18f/0x420; page_fault+0x1f/0x30; 0x200007ea; 0xffffffffffffffff\n\nI'm going to test with just this patch pulled off master, but I think we've got a significant regression here.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "ad82a0694f282f0878b917892a0995977f9f16c8",
      "author": {
