        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2014-01-28 22:52:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nReverting only this patch did not seem to resolve the hang described previously.  I'm going to revert to the version of master I'm sure was good - I think Wednesday last week - and then may do bisecting to find the problematic commit if time permits.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
